<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome - Cooperative Banking</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #1976d2;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #1976d2;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .features {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>{{bankName}}</h1>
        <h2>Welcome to Cooperative Banking!</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
        
        <p>Welcome to {{bankName}}! We're excited to have you as a member of our cooperative banking family.</p>
        
        <p>Your account has been successfully created and you can now access all our banking services.</p>
        
        <div class="features">
            <h3>What you can do:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>✅ View your account balance and transaction history</li>
                <li>✅ Transfer money between accounts</li>
                <li>✅ Deposit and withdraw funds</li>
                <li>✅ Apply for loans and other financial products</li>
                <li>✅ Access 24/7 online banking</li>
                <li>✅ Get personalized financial advice</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p>Click the button below to log in to your account:</p>
        
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Log In to Your Account</a>
        
        <p><strong>Security Tips:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Never share your login credentials with anyone</li>
            <li>Always log out when you're done banking</li>
            <li>Use strong, unique passwords</li>
            <li>Enable two-factor authentication if available</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our customer support team is here to help.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        {{bankName}} Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>© 2024 {{bankName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
